        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Broadband Equipment Rental Reform Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a broadband internet provider from charging a consumer for the rental, lease, or provision of equipment if the consumer has paid the purchase price of such equipment through monthly rental fees. </p>]]>
        </text>
